IRAF - Image Reduction and Analytic Functions

Balik, vyvijeny na NOAO (National Optical Astronomy Observatories), patrici \
AURA (Association of Universities for Research in Astronomy), ve spolupraci \
s NSF (National Science Foundation).

Stoji za vetsinou snimku z Hubble Space Telescope.

