ESO-Midas

European South Observatory - Munich Image Data Analytic System

Balik, vyvijen v Mnichove pro ESO. Preveden pod open-source. 

%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
%page

Plus/minus:

+ privetive uzivatelske rozhranni
+ dostatek dokumentace, snadna orientace v ni
+ nenarocnost na systemove prostredky

- spatne propojeni na DAOPHOT
- tezkopadnost definice promennych
- komplikovany a pomerne slaby vnitrni jazyk

